{"tid":2417812,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點可以專心做野/讀書","createTime":"2021-02-22T07:14:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T09:14:06.000Z","uid":336524,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a7908a67689dd22a5bcb10e43990ffbbbeba60ba","tid":2417812,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T07:14:41.000Z","msg":"呢排個人完全專心唔到做野/ 學野<br />\n一掂啲工作同埋學術野就想去打機/ 碌手機<br />\n好彩呢排年尾年頭個個都清假，公司無乜人，而且個個都無咩心機做野，所以我都一樣無乜野做<br />\n<br />\n但係自己有啲cert 考緊，完全專心唔到溫書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自己好似有個loop:<br />\n<br />\n一段時期對打機/social media 0興趣，淨係想專心做野、學新野。（可以係幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n一段時段完全唔想做野，淨係想瘋狂打機，瘋狂碌手機。玩到厭又會去返上一個階段。<br />\n<br />\n有無人都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n定係我呢排對打機上左癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7c3e1d48cda1ae51fb81900113979f3140df427","tid":2417812,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T07:18:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c69742327f99d9cc501419dd5952da59248fcf54","tid":2417812,"uid":388778,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T07:18:28.000Z","msg":"咁你打機嗰陣會唔會想讀書"},{"pid":"c6273f2ba191e66f2d44834fb53f64c20a1afebb","tid":2417812,"uid":38904,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T07:23:52.000Z","msg":"證明你唔係讀書嘅材料"},{"pid":"24279bd97f3ec24edc6cbad30d7c25456df46e11","tid":2417812,"uid":64576,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T07:24:32.000Z","msg":"證明你對個樣野唔係真係有興趣"},{"pid":"00441ff101fb0aa6765401ce36e87b09ed3912eb","tid":2417812,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c69742327f99d9cc501419dd5952da59248fcf54","tid":2417812,"uid":388778,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T07:18:28.000Z","msg":"咁你打機嗰陣會唔會想讀書"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T07:26:37.000Z","msg":"依家唔會<br />\n之前會 <br />\n<br />\n之前個排雖然對打機無興趣，但因為做野/溫書搞到好攰所以都有玩下啲ps4單機game放鬆下。個陣時真係會一路玩一路諗啲讀書野/工作idea<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家諗起工作/讀書野就覺得煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2983fcc1015dfcb21cec34383f48a721abf72dc0","tid":2417812,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"24279bd97f3ec24edc6cbad30d7c25456df46e11","tid":2417812,"uid":64576,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T07:24:32.000Z","msg":"證明你對個樣野唔係真係有興趣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T07:30:59.000Z","msg":"感覺自己係對打機上左癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nPs4 火影忍者終極風暴4 好好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多角色玩 啲角色嘅忍術、招式又還原得好<br />\n玩到上晒癮咁<br />\n<br />\n好想快啲返屋企開機試多啲角色嘅技能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個心好囉囉攣，好似上左癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7bf956b57f0037754d6ee9e3bbe22b29aef5cf2","tid":2417812,"uid":287107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2983fcc1015dfcb21cec34383f48a721abf72dc0","tid":2417812,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"24279bd97f3ec24edc6cbad30d7c25456df46e11","tid":2417812,"uid":64576,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T07:24:32.000Z","msg":"證明你對個樣野唔係真係有興趣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T07:30:59.000Z","msg":"感覺自己係對打機上左癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nPs4 火影忍者終極風暴4 好好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多角色玩 啲角色嘅忍術、招式又還原得好<br />\n玩到上